BRANIFF'S
BUSINESS CABIN™ SERVICE
At last, first-rate treatment for our regular coach fare customers.
Our Business Cabin™ means:
• A separate forward cabin.
• More legroom than regular coach.
• Middle seats that can fold down when space permits, to
create an executive work area.
• New, more comfortable seats in cool, soft Nutra® leather.
• Excellent meal service with complimentary French wines.
Economy Cabin:™ Low Fares,
Great Service
The Braniff Economy Cabin™ is designed for travelers who
can plan ahead and take advantage of special lower fares—
with many of the Business Cabin™ extras. Add Braniff's
commitment to outstanding service and you won't find a
better value anywhere.
Braniff Business Club: A Special
Place For Braniff Travelers
Relax in the Braniff Business Club, opposite Gate 16 at Dallas/
Fort Worth Regional Airport. It features complimentary coffee,
tea and snacks, free local calls, round trip check-in facilities,
private conference rooms, newspapers, magazines and tele-
vision, a bar and lounge, plus personal check cashing through
the Club desk.
While admission to the Braniff Business Club is by membership
only, members may bring guests. More detailed information
and applications are available at the Club desk or any Braniff
ticket counter at the Dallas/Fort Worth Regional Airport.
The Braniff Business Club. Just another way Braniff serves
you better.
Mileage Plus
Braniff and United Airlines have joined forces on the Mileage
Plus program. Now you can earn miles on both carriers. And
Braniff travelers will be able to take advantage of periodic
Mileage Plus specials. In addition, our Mileage Plus program
will give you access to Lufthansa, SAS, Air New Zealand and
Air France, as well as exotic destinations like Hawaii, Tokyo, or
Hong Kong. Not to mention Royal Viking Line cruises to areas
like the Caribbean.
1-800-BRANIFF
For reservations or more information, call our easy to-remember
TOLL-FREE number: 1-800-BRANIFF. Or in Dallas, call 357-9511.
In Fort Worth, call 261-2442. And remember, you've got a
lot of good reasons to fly Braniff.
BRAMIFF
